      "comment_id" : 85639737,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "It is not required. In my case, <code>$JAVA_HOME</code> refers <code>$(&#47;usr&#47;libexec&#47;java_home)</code> and <code>$(&#47;usr&#47;libexec&#47;java_home)</code>   is internally referred as <code>&#47;Library&#47;Java&#47;JavaVirtualMachines&#47;jdk1.8.0_131.jdk&#47;Contents&#47;&zwnj;&#8203;Home</code> by the System."
